West 131st Street, at, adjoining and east of the S.E. corner of Old Broadway (right) as viewed westward.

No. 538 is a two story frame house separating the corner property (No. 67 Old Broadway) from the stone garage (No. 536 West 131st Street). At the right margin appears a portion of the old frame building at the S.W. corner, bearing No's. 66 Old Broadway and 570 West 131st Street.

View No. 2 is limited and shows solely No. 538, the frame dwelling aforementioned.

View 1: April 1, 1938

P. L. Sperr

J. Clarence Davies Collection
Museum of The City of New York

View 2: 1932
